Hey guys so the first thing I did in 0.25 was make a new version of my old biplane with the new parts, this one has more lift, more speed and is super-maneuverable :D

Let me know what you think, this has got to be one of my most fun planes to fly, not sure if I should put a thrust limiter on it, not sure if it would save fuel going slower??
